  "SubGoals": [],
  "Description": "This Goal initiates a test for asking a question via Nostr messaging. It begins by notifying that the test is starting and sets a timeout for waiting for a response. The goal then asks the user for their favorite color and stores the response. If no response is received within the specified time, an error is thrown. If a response is received, it confirms the successful routing of the ask through Nostr.",
